header.description: Property. This message contains a compressed image  Header timestamp should be acquisition time of image

format.description: Property.  Header frame_id should be optical frame of camera  origin of frame should be optical center of camera  +x should point to the right in the image  +y should point down in the image  +z should point into to plane of the image  Specifies the format of the data

data.description: Property.    Acceptable values:      jpeg, png  Compressed image buffer
